<p>Through writing, I want to: Learn more effectively and efficiently by taking notes and chunking my thoughts Understand and be able to articulate what I&#8217;m thinking Keep notes for future reflection and time travel Connect with people who have similar interests Help other people save time I&#8217;m pretty happy with how I&#8217;m doing this so [&#8230;]</p>
